Symbol.Script_3D:
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then END
if gs_shadow=0 then SHADOW OFF
pen gs_cont_pen
if iType = RECTANGULAR then addy b rotx 90 if ABS(gs_frame_width)<EPS & same_thk then cprism_ smat,smat,gs_frame_mat,5,b, 0,0,15, a,0,15, a,zzyzx,15, 0,zzyzx,15, 0,0,-1 else material gs_frame_mat if bFrameLeft then ! Left prism_ 5,b, 0, 0, 15, p_th_left, p_th_low, 15, p_th_left, zzyzx-p_th_up, 15, 0, zzyzx, 15, 0, 0, -1 endif
if bFrameRight then ! Right prism_ 5, b, a, 0, 15, a, zzyzx, 15, a-p_th_right, zzyzx-p_th_up,15, a-p_th_right, p_th_low, 15, a, 0, -1 endif
base vert 0, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 0, 0, 1 vert 1, 0, 0 coor 2 + 256, -1, -2, -3, -4 body -1
if bFrameLower then ! Lower prism_ 5,b, 0, 0, 15, a, 0, 15, a-p_th_right, p_th_low, 15, p_th_left, p_th_low, 15, 0, 0, -1 endif
if bFrameUpper then ! Upper prism_ 5,b, 0, zzyzx,15, a, zzyzx,15, a-p_th_right, zzyzx-p_th_up,15, p_th_left, zzyzx-p_th_up,15, 0, zzyzx,-1 endif
base vert 0, 0, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 0, 0, 1 coor 2 + 256, -1, -2, -3, -4 body -1
material smat
addz b/6 prism_ 5,b*4/6, p_th_left,p_th_low,15, a-p_th_right,p_th_low,15, a-p_th_right,zzyzx-p_th_up,15, p_th_left,zzyzx-p_th_up,15, p_th_left,p_th_low,-1 del 1 endif
del 2 endif
if iType = ROUND then zmer=a hotspot 0,-b,zmer hotspot 0,0,zmer hotspot a,-b,zmer hotspot a,0,zmer hotspot a/2,-b,zmer hotspot a/2,0,zmer
add a/2,b,a/2 rotx 90 resol gs_resol
if bFrame then material gs_frame_mat
prism_ 14, B, a/2, 0, 79, 0, 0, 900, 0.0, 180.0, 4000, -a/2, 0, 79, 0, 0, 900, 0, 180.0, 4001, a/2, 0.0, -1,
a/2-gs_frame_width, 0, 79, 0, 0, 900, 0.0, 180.0, 4000, -a/2+gs_frame_width, 0, 79, 0, 0, 900, 0, 180.0, 4001, a/2-gs_frame_width, 0.0, -1 base rotz 90 vert 0, 0, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 0, 0, 1 del 1 coor 2 + 256, -1, -2, -3, -4 body -1 endif
material smat
prism_ 7, B/6, a/2-gs_frame_width, 0, 79, 0, 0, 900, 0.0, 180.0, 4000, -a/2+gs_frame_width, 0, 79, 0, 0, 900, 0, 180.0, 4001, a/2-gs_frame_width, 0.0, -1 del 2 endif
if iType = ELLIPTIC then add a/2,b,zzyzx/2 rotx 90 resol gs_resol
n=0 for x=0 to 360 step 7.5 n=n+1 put (a/2-gs_frame_width)*cos(x), (zzyzx/2-gs_frame_width)*sin(x), 79 next x
material smat prism_ n, b*4/6, get(nsp)
if bFrame then material gs_frame_mat
nn=0 for x=0 to 375 step 7.5 nn=nn+1 put (a/2-gs_frame_width)*cos(x), (zzyzx/2-gs_frame_width)*sin(x), 0, 0 next x
tube 4, nn, 0, 0, 0, 0, -gs_frame_width, 0, 0, -gs_frame_width, b, 0, 0, b, 0, get(nsp) base rotz 90 vert 0, 0, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 0, 0, 1 del 1 coor 2 + 256, -1, -2, -3, -4 body -1 del 1 endif endif end
Symbol.Script_2D:
pen gs_cont_pen
hotspot2 a/2,b
CALL "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" parameters ALL
rect2 0,0,a,b
fill gs_fill_type
poly2_b 5, 1+2+4+64,gs_fill_pen,gs_back_pen, 0,0,1, a,0,1, a,b,1, 0,b,1, 0,0,-1
Symbol.Script_1D:
EPS = 0.0001
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2 DLEV3D_DRAFT = 3
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m RECTANGULAR = 1 ROUND = 2 ELLIPTIC = 3
if zzyzx<0.1 then zzyzx=0.1
if iType <> RECTANGULAR then same_thk=1
if same_thk then if (bFrame) then p_th_up = gs_frame_width p_th_low = gs_frame_width p_th_right = gs_frame_width p_th_left = gs_frame_width else p_th_up = 0 p_th_low = 0 p_th_right = 0 p_th_left = 0 endif
bFrameUpper = bFrame bFrameLower = bFrame bFrameRight = bFrame bFrameLeft = bFrame else if not(bFrameUpper) then p_th_up = 0 if not(bFrameLower) then p_th_low = 0 if not(bFrameRight) then p_th_right = 0 if not(bFrameLeft) then p_th_left = 0 endif
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
!Hide all parameters from UI hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
values "a" range [0.1,) values "b" range [0.01,) values "zzyzx" range [0.1,)
values "gs_frame_width" range (, min(abs(a/2-0.01),abs(zzyzx/2-0.01))) values "p_th_up" range (, abs(zzyzx/2)) values "p_th_low" range (, abs(zzyzx/2)) values "p_th_right" range (, abs(a/2)) values "p_th_left" range (, abs(a/2))
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.`
values{2} "iType" RECTANGULAR, `Прямоугольное`, ROUND, `Круглое`, ELLIPTIC, `Эллиптическое`
values "gs_resol" range [3,)
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=4 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=19
values "gs_frame_width" range [0,)
if same_thk then hideparameter "p_th_up","p_th_low","p_th_right","p_th_left" lock "p_th_up","p_th_low","p_th_right","p_th_left" else hideparameter "gs_frame_width" lock "gs_frame_width" endif
if not(bFrameUpper) then hideparameter "p_th_up" lock "p_th_up" endif
if not(bFrameLower) then hideparameter "p_th_low" lock "p_th_low" endif
if not(bFrameRight) then hideparameter "p_th_right" lock "p_th_right" endif
if not(bFrameLeft) then hideparameter "p_th_left" lock "p_th_left" endif
if iType = RECTANGULAR then lock "gs_resol" if iType <> RECTANGULAR then hideparameter "same_thk","bFrameUpper", "bFrameLower", "bFrameRight", "bFrameLeft" lock "same_thk","bFrameUpper", "bFrameLower", "bFrameRight", "bFrameLeft" endif if iType = ROUND then lock "zzyzx"
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow"

Symbol.Script_FWM:
actualGUID = FROM_GUID
! ============================================================================== ! Subroutines ! ==============================================================================
_autoID = "9D1ED332-F770-422D-A760-CF2F9DB84D22" _startID = "B43F3F2E-A900-48C0-A32E-F7C21FD0DC4A" _endID = "C0551B28-4116-4FEF-A6B8-BB7762BDF7AA" gosub "newparameters_FWM"
! ============================================================================== ! Set migration GUID ! ==============================================================================
setmigrationguid actualGUID
! ============================================================================== end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! en ! ==============================================================================
! ============================================================================== ! New Parameters_iType_bFrameUpper_bFrameLower_bFrameRight_bFrameLeft ! ============================================================================== "newparameters_FWM": if actualGuid = _startID | actualGuid = _autoID then
bHas = DELETED_PAR_VALUE("gs_typ", _gs_typ)
if _gs_typ = 1 then ! Rectangular iType = 1 else if _gs_typ = 2 then ! Round iType = 2 else ! Elliptic iType = 3 endif endif
parameters iType = iType
bHas = STORED_PAR_VALUE ("p_th_up", _p_th_up) |\ STORED_PAR_VALUE ("p_th_low", _p_th_low) |\ STORED_PAR_VALUE ("p_th_right", _p_th_right) |\ STORED_PAR_VALUE ("p_th_left", _p_th_left) |\ STORED_PAR_VALUE ("gs_frame_width", _gs_frame_width)
! if Mirror Frame Width is 0 then Frame is off if iType = 1 then ! Rectangular if _gs_frame_width > EPS or (_p_th_up > EPS and _p_th_low > EPS and _p_th_right > EPS and _p_th_left > EPS) then bFrame = 1 else bFrame = 0 endif
else ! Round, Elliptic if _gs_frame_width > EPS then bFrame = 1 else bFrame = 0 endif endif
! if Upper Frame Thickness is 0 then Frame Upper is off if _p_th_up > EPS then bFrameUpper = 1 else bFrameUpper = 0 endif
! if Lower Frame Thickness is 0 then Frame Lower is off if _p_th_low > EPS then bFrameLower = 1 else bFrameLower = 0 endif
! if Right Frame Thicknes is 0 then Frame on Side 1 is off if _p_th_right > EPS then bFrameRight = 1 else bFrameRight = 0 endif
! if Left Frame Thicknes is 0 then Frame on Side 2 is off if _p_th_left > EPS then bFrameLeft = 1 else bFrameLeft = 0 endif
parameters bFrameUpper = bFrameUpper, bFrameLower = bFrameLower, bFrameRight = bFrameRight, bFrameLeft = bFrameLeft actualGuid = _endID endif return
Symbol.Script_BWM:
targetGUID = TO_GUID
! ============================================================================== ! Subroutines ! ==============================================================================
gosub "newparameters_BWM"
! ============================================================================== ! Set migration GUID ! ==============================================================================
setmigrationguid targetGuid
! ============================================================================== end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! en ! ==============================================================================
! ============================================================================== ! New Parameters_ ! ============================================================================== "newparameters_BWM": if targetGUID # "" then newparameter "gs_typ", "Integer" newparameter "typ", "String"
if iType = 1 then gs_typ = 1 typ = `Прямоугольное` endif
if iType = 2 then gs_typ = 2 typ = `Круглое` endif
if iType = 3 then gs_typ = 3 typ = `Эллиптическое` endif
parameters gs_typ = gs_typ typ = typ
! if Frame is off then Mirror Frame Width is 0 if gs_typ = 1 then ! Rectangular if not(bFrame) then gs_frame_width = 0 else gs_frame_width = gs_frame_width endif else ! Round, Elliptic if not(bFrame) then gs_frame_width = 0 p_th_up = 0 p_th_low = 0 p_th_right = 0 p_th_left = 0 else gs_frame_width = gs_frame_width p_th_up = p_th_up p_th_low = p_th_low p_th_right = p_th_right p_th_left = p_th_left endif endif
! if Frame Upper is off then Upper Frame Thickness is 0 if not(bFrameUpper) then p_th_up = 0 else p_th_up = p_th_up endif
! if Frame Lower is off then Lower Frame Thickness is 0 if not(bFrameLower) then p_th_low = 0 else p_th_low = p_th_low endif
! if Frame on Side 1 is off then Right Frame Thickness is 0 if not(bFrameRight) then p_th_right = 0 else p_th_right = p_th_right endif
! if Frame on Side 2 is off then Left Frame Thickness is 0 if not(bFrameLeft) then p_th_left = 0 else p_th_left = p_th_left endif
parameters p_th_up = p_th_up, p_th_low = p_th_low, p_th_right = p_th_right, p_th_left = p_th_left, gs_frame_width = gs_frame_width endif return
